explain select * from t1 where match(name) against ('SQL') or year > 1990;
Query Plan
=================================================================
|ID|OPERATOR                    |NAME     |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
-----------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |DISTRIBUTED INDEX MERGE SCAN|t1(i1,i3)|12      |2316        |
=================================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
