===================================================
|ID|OPERATOR           |NAME|EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
---------------------------------------------------
|0 |NESTED-LOOP JOIN   |    |1       |105         |
|1 |├─TABLE FULL SCAN  |b   |1       |3           |
|2 |└─MATERIAL         |    |1       |3           |
|3 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN|a   |1       |3           |
===================================================
Outputs & filters:
-------------------------------------
  0 - output([a.c1], [a.c3], [b.c1]), filter(nil), rowset=2
      conds([a.c1 = 5 OR a.c3 < 390000 AND MATCH(b.c4) AGAINST('鄂A1')], [a.c2 = b.c2]), nl_params_(nil), use_batch=false
  1 - output([b.c1], [b.c2], [MATCH(b.c4) AGAINST('鄂A1')]), filter(nil), rowset=2
      access([b.c1], [b.c2]), partitions(p0)
      is_index_back=false, is_global_index=false, 
      range_key([b.c1]), range(MIN ; MAX)always true, has_functional_lookup=true
  2 - output([a.c1], [a.c3], [a.c2], [a.c1 = 5], [a.c3 < 390000]), filter(nil), rowset=2
